{"tid":1584700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【極重要】推比手足睇 撤退時記得要反跟蹤","createTime":"2019-09-21T09:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T06:32:06.000Z","uid":89966,"like":290,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":156,"replies":[{"pid":"d706219f5651cb3344452a57b31523fe413fbe87","tid":1584700,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T09:19:52.000Z","msg":"From上星期九龍灣拘捕行動<br />\nHK01記者：<br />\n收到消息指警方改變策略，為防前線爆出太多暴力畫面，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>改由便衣跟蹤</strong></span>暴力示威者回家才拘捕，暫有消息指有不少拘捕發生在九龍。要等到明天警察記招再求證。<br />\n<br />\n上車行多兩卡混入人群再落車洗一轉底撇甩<br />\n轉多幾程車唔好係大站落車<br />\n就算變左裝都好 都唔好鬆懈 特別係上過鏡高危動作既手足們！！！"},{"pid":"10289d17d5cf47e3b1735bfcd32027b4fd8b255b","tid":1584700,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T09:20:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"f5be129e62d78bfada227a1c5cd57c84a570e846","tid":1584700,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T09:20:30.000Z","msg":"推1/100"},{"pid":"3e2afa15c4538885612ce62ef1e5cb44caefeaa3","tid":1584700,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T09:20:38.000Z","msg":"[行動又無人理？] 全球最大親子抗爭活動上線啦！ <strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">#birdfoldingchallenge</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1584614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1584614</a><br />\n摺一隻紙鳥，影相，放上Facebook / Twitter / Instagram，並加上hashtag #birdfoldingchallenge #929globalmarch #929GlobalAntiTotalitarianism，copy呢段文字再tag 5個朋友，就完成！</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iYhkXcO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiYhkXcO.jpg&h=9b11593e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ee99e6309b90c567a8cae7d29a8b3383c86dbf