"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:14:27.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n散水請小心"},{"pid":"41bb039526072dad850dea7193f3048fc75a58f4","tid":1584700,"uid":40880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:14:54.000Z","msg":"Credit: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1569544/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1569544/page/1</a><br />\n例如上巴士扮搵散紙，等d人差唔多上哂車就落車<br />\n<br />\n例如坐黨鐵，到下一個站關門前落車，等下一班，安全d可以本身坐個方向同返屋企方向唔同，落車後再去對面線坐返屋企<br />\n<br />\n例如入商場行入少少，轉身再出商場，轉去多人嘅地方，再再次轉返入商場，由商場另一個門口出<br />\n<br />\n例如去到路口轉左行一段路，再突然向後跑另一邊<br />\n總之大家睇下反跟蹤係點做<br />\n最重要係反跟蹤過程要留意身邊嘅人"},{"pid":"50c76273d1be42dfeca521894a8aa6fb870c0cd3","tid":1584700,"uid":325214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:14:56.000Z","msg":"P牌照推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74dc9beb8a7bbdae3207da961e538959a2ad5949","tid":1584700,"uid":52424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d287823db75b278d8357a19a15fead4a0b979a","tid":1584700,"uid":181521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb6a06f98b49955353a720f93bae080664e68e2","tid":1584700,"uid":164317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:19:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4ccfbf892344dacb98969524b4a796197c5b8c9","tid":1584700,"uid":143371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:20:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"754a573a8852a4ac00ecb88a6a3373e4c3206a07","tid":1584700,"uid":250689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:21:13.000Z","msg":"推 手足小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dr